{"tid":662362,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"上星期整親條腰 痛撚到而家","createTime":"2018-05-12T11:12:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-18T15:59:50.000Z","uid":98507,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"df055ac86dd47801cb239c4903455c6e60ccb31c","tid":662362,"uid":98507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T11:12:19.000Z","msg":"話說上星期六搬屋<br />\n見個衣櫃訓底左 我諗住托返直佢<br />\n點知托嗰下CHOK親條腰<br />\n痛完星期六 星期日見唔係好痛 都有繼續搬屋<br />\n我諗應該就快冇野<br />\n點知到左前日開始越黎越痛 咳一咳都痛<br />\n咁咪自己搵藥酒捽下同貼d藥膏 但好似冇乜效<br />\n尋日去照x光又唔見有問題 醫生話可能拉傷姐<br />\n到左今日...行行下街直情頂唔順跪底左<br />\n走去睇中藥佢話膊頭d力卸左落腰搞到整親<br />\n佢幫我捽完之後仲痛過未捽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n痛到我連挺直個身都做唔到<br />\n<br />\n點算 我係咪玩完喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99e7bc9c17d0f7b2b010f4e506ef1491ce8aa099","tid":662362,"uid":24997,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T11:23:47.000Z","msg":"老左你就知<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7febc60b7f598346a9cda6d11bba5d75f6368e6","tid":662362,"uid":98507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99e7bc9c17d0f7b2b010f4e506ef1491ce8aa099","tid":662362,"uid":24997,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T11:23:47.000Z","msg":"老左你就知<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T11:30:33.000Z","msg":"風濕？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唉，而家都未好返，唔知點樣搞"},{"pid":"26506de321f4bfabd58dbbca066c508fed197b8e","tid":662362,"uid":13738,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"df055ac86dd47801cb239c4903455c6e60ccb31c","tid":662362,"uid":98507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T11:12:19.000Z","msg":"話說上星期六搬